  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2007-10-24",
    "date": "2007-11-29T21:58:52Z",
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase to $5,000 the maximum dollar amount of the child tax credit for the surviving spouse and children of a member of the Armed Forces who dies while serving in a combat zone; and (2) waive the adjusted gross income limitation applicable to the child tax credit for such military families."
